snippet.title: The Channel F Files Podcast Video Supplemental Videocart #3 BlackJack!
snippet.description: Lets play some BlackJack on that Channel F!  Another first done by the Fairchild Channel F was to bring a BlackJack game to the TV screen.  Very well done and quite playable!
